        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer11538981" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5756978496672774927">The end of this book horribly disappointed me. Reading two-thirds of a beautifully written book supporting atheism raised me to a delightful level of happiness. Which was swiftly destroyed by the chapter on atheistic mystical experiences. What a crock. What about life without transcendence? </span>

          </span>
        </div>


