<span id="freeTextContainer11437502443157817451">I struggled with this book and finally gave up in the middle of the chapter on the existence of God. I found the essay dense and boring. As promised, there was some humor in what I read, but not enough to propel me to the finish. Perhaps I&apos;ll pick it up again in a few years and have another crack at it.</span>
  <span id="freeText11437502443157817451" style="display:none">I struggled with this book and finally gave up in the middle of the chapter on the existence of God. I found the essay dense and boring. As promised, there was some humor in what I read, but not enough to propel me to the finish. Perhaps I'll pick it up again in a few years and have another crack at it.</span>
